I thought about what I would write for this post for a couple months and I went back and forth between an emotional one or a nonchalant. But I think I got all the deep emotions out because When I put my petition in to graduate about two months ago I was in the counselors office and she submitted it, tears started LEAKING down my face I couldn’t control it. I have tried going to school a few times and life circumstances got in the way. I just couldn’t believe I finally got here. I love everyone who came out in support of me today. Especially my family coming out to LA to watch me walk and my sister in Italy watched on FaceTime: Here’s to going further !! 🌸💕👩🏻‍🎓 sorry I just am obsessed with this song and THIS IS THE BEST PART!!! I love my friends so much only they know just went I went through while obtaining this goal of mine. 😅
